      <h3>
  
    
      <a href="http://westvanlibrary.ca/events/friday-night-concert-vancouver-opera-young-artists-program">Vancouver Opera Young Artists </a>
      </h3>
  

      <div class="featured-body">
  
    
      <span>Combining charming stories with music from Candide, Roméo et Juliette, Rigoletto, Carmen and Jekyll and Hyde, this Friday Night Concert will delight and enthral! March 18, 7:30 p.m.</span>
<span class="more-link"><a href="http://westvanlibrary.ca/events/friday-night-concert-vancouver-opera-young-artists-program">More</a></span>
      </div>
  
    </div>
      <div class="row even">
      
      <div class="taxonomy-image">
  
    
      <img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://westvanlibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/thumbnail/public/images/features/terms/comm.png?itok=6gusqnDS" width="100" height="100" alt="" />
      </div>
  

      <h3>
  
    
      Friends of the Library Spring Booksale
      </h3>
  

      <div class="featured-body">
  
    
      Stock up on books and find some great bargains! Members Pre-Sale, Thursday, April 7. Memberships available at the door for $10. Public Sale is Friday, April 8 and Saturday, April 9, 10 a.m. – 4 p.m.
<span class="more-link"></span>
      </div>
  
    </div>
