      </div>
  

      <h3>
  
    
      <a href="https://westvanlibrary.ca/research-learn/learn/online-courses-lectures">Learn with Lynda</a>
      </h3>
  

      <div class="featured-body">
  
    
      With the launch of Lynda.com, thousands of online training courses are now available for anyone looking to learn new computer, business, presentation, design and other skills. Just use your library card! 
<span class="more-link"><a href="https://westvanlibrary.ca/research-learn/learn/online-courses-lectures">More</a></span>
      </div>
  
    </div>
